{"tid":173468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老，藍屍與斯德哥爾摩綜合症","createTime":"2017-03-26T08:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T08:24:47.000Z","uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09aa3308748b3231dd4f936932c5c16d8db13f0f","tid":173468,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%96%AF%E5%BE%B7%E5%93%A5%E7%88%BE%E6%91%A9%E7%97%87%E5%80%99%E7%BE%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%2593%25A5%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%2591%25A9%25E7%2597%2587%25E5%2580%2599%25E7%25BE%25A4&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=0df9cc1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%96%AF%E5%BE%B7%E5%93%A5%E7%88%BE%E6%91%A9%E7%97%87%E5%80%99%E7%BE%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n出現斯德哥爾摩綜合症的人質，通常有下列幾項特徵：<br />\n1.綁匪為了某種原因而綁架人質，並得到人質認同。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">＞＞廢老，藍屍</span><br />\n<br />\n2.人質必須有真正感到綁匪（加害者）威脅到自己的存活。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">＞＞廢老，藍屍之冇支那冇香港論</span><br />\n<br />\n3.在遭挾持過程中，人質必須體會出綁匪（加害者）可能略施小惠的舉動。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">＞＞廢老，藍屍眼中嘅支那所謂嘅恩惠</span><br />\n<br />\n4.除了綁匪的單一看法之外，人質必須與所有其他觀點隔離（通常得不到外界的訊息）。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">＞＞CCTVB</span><br />\n<br />\n5.人質必須相信，要脫逃是不可能的。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">＞＞廢老，藍屍眼中嘅支那強大論</span>"}]}